3. cs.COM (Computers and Society) - The paper discusses the societal impact of 6G technologies, such as the potential for new applications and services. 
4. cs.AR (Augmented Reality) - The paper speculates on the visionary technologies that could enable 6G, which could include augmented reality technologies. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper discusses the potential for new multimedia applications and services enabled by 6G technologies.
